title: The TraxNYC Interview: How He Broke into The Jewelry Business, 6ix9ine Scamming Him & More
description:
TraxNYC learned the business by himself, worked hard and entered every room with good intentions. Today he's calling out jewelry sellers doing bad business and try to scam him! Plus, explains how 6ix9ine and Scott Disick stole from him and how he flipped it into a marketing opportunity.
